The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for event factuality prediction. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses neural models, which suggests that it could belong to sub-categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with improving performance on datasets, which could suggest sub-categories such as cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
